===Adjective===
'''[[packed]] [[decimal]]'''
#(''computing'') A [[storage]] [[mode]] that places two [[decimal]] [[digit]]s into one [[byte]], each digit occupying four [[bit]]s. The [[sign]] occupies four bits in the [[least]] [[significant]] byte; defined as COMP-3 in [[COBOL]]

